queries.query: SELECT metric_name as "x_axis_1"  FROM "aws_introspection_rds_metrics"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT namespace as "x_axis_1"  FROM "aws_introspection_rds_metrics"  GROUP BY x_axis_1
SELECT histogram(_timestamp) as "x_axis_1", max(max) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "aws_introspection_rds_metrics"  WHERE metric_name IN ('FreeableMemory')  GROUP BY x_axis_1 ORDER BY x_axis_1 ASC
SELECT histogram(_timestamp) as "x_axis_1", max(max) as "y_axis_1"  FROM "aws_introspection_rds_metrics"  WHERE metric_name LIKE '%DatabaseConnections%'  GROUP BY x_axis_1 ORDER BY x_axis_1 ASC
